%Publishing Toolbox%%Routines for manipulating figures, labels and axes for publication-quality figures.%Contents:%--Axes manipulation%xtoff, ytoff: turn the x or y ticks off on the current axes%xtloff, ytloff: turn the x or y tick labels off on the current axes%%--Labeling%textbox: place a box with text at a specified location%tb, tbr: place bold-face text, with or without arrows for pointing.%ScootLabel: move an axes label up or down.%%Symbols: definitions of common label strings.%%--graphics manipulation:%lw: set the line width of a plot.%lc: set the color of a plot.%%--axes and figure manipulation:%wysiwyg, wys75: make the screen appearance of the figure like what will print%aguonecolumn: set figure defaults for an agu-size one-col figure%myaguonecolumn: same as above, but allow a horizontal offset.%agutwocolumn: set figure defaults for an agu-size two-col figure%%--Default settings%PresentationDefaults: set font sizes, etc for slides.